      <h2>Weaving the APA Integrative Themes <em>throughout</em></h2>
      <p>Rather than treating the APA Themes as a checklist item, I built them into the fabric of each module. They show up in the Readiness Check pages and Background You&rsquo;ll Need sections at the start of every module, where students can see right away how the content connects to bigger ideas in psychology and in their own lives. The themes aren&rsquo;t just mentioned &mdash; they&rsquo;re actively used to frame the learning.</p>

